data.description: Remodeled and updated home used as a short term rental is ready for its new investor or home owner! Everything in the home is included in the sale except door keypad and security cameras. Home has a beautifully, updated kitchen with open space from the front to the back of the house. Screened porch in the front with a great sized deck and garden in the back! There are two designated parking spaces in the back and space in the drive way for at least one car. It also has a metal, long lasting roof. This home makes $2,500+ from 30+ day renters and will also be perfect for an end buyer!
